data.description: Brand New Roof Coming!  (Feb 2024)  Welcome Home to this stately Colonial in Chantilly Highlands.  RECEIVED SIGHT UNSEEN OFFER - UNDER CONTRACT.   Chantilly High School Pyramid.   This 4 bedroom/2.5 bathroom home features a spacious center hall foyer with generously sized living room and dining room. Other models have used ones of these spaces as a main level office. The kitchen has been updated with new appliances, new granite counters, new sink and faucet! The family room has a gas fireplace and the room is far more spacious than the typical colonial - tons of room to even add a home office or game table/homework spot!  Upstairs features four bedrooms and two bathrooms - all freshly painted. The main level and upstairs are hardwood floors!  The basement level is unfinished and has rough in plumbing (a money saver for later!) and ready for your design ideas and instant equity! A perfect indoor play area for kids until you are ready to finish it! The backyard has a deck that has been freshly repainted and a fully fenced backyard.   Per owner - Roof (2024),  HVAC (2016),  New Counters and Kitchen Appliances (2023).  Seller would prefer 30-60 day rent back.  Photos will be uploaded on February 15th.
